  "markup": "Join Douglas Johnson, ATC as he shares the latest research and clinical insights on super pulsed laser therapy for the reduction of non-specific knee pain.\u003Cbr /\u003E\nWeak at the knees\u0026hellip;explore strategies for the reduction of both acute and chronic knee pain\u003Cbr /\u003E\nAdding to the mix \u0026ndash; review how PBM can be a clinically significant addition to your current treatment plan\u003Cbr /\u003E\nGetting it done\u0026hellip;The best protocol to address knee pain."
}]]></Value>
